  "title": "Senior Abacus Trainer | Yishun - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Abacus Trainer </strong></p><p>Working Days: 6 Days (Off on Monday)<br />Working hours are as below:<br />* Tues @ 12.30pm - 9.30pm (Before passing Teacher's Evaluation)<br />* Tues @ 4.30pm - 9.30pm (After passing Teacher's Evaluation)<br />* Wed - Fri @ 12.30pm - 9.30pm<br />* Sat @ 10.15am - 7.15pm<br />* Sun @ 10.15am - 6.15pm<br />Working Location: Yishun<br />Salary: $3000 to $4000 (Based on experience and qualification)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />Conduct structured abacus-mental arithmetic lessons (physical & online) for children aged 3–12.<br />Ensure lesson delivery, classroom management, and parent communication.<br />Guide junior trainers during onboarding and certification.<br />Provide feedback to improve teaching methodology and curriculum content.<br />Participate in internal trainer workshops and assist in training sessions.<br />Assist in centre events, competitions, and outreach initiatives as required.</p><p><strong>Requirements: </strong><br />Diploma or Degree holder (or equivalent qualification).<br />Minimum 2 years of abacus mental arithmetic teaching experience.<br /></p><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
